/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/670_7.2.0.xml#_d47a330b-01d8-40a0-9387-8d50ef1bfa46" id="_34f44a4a-c379-48f7-a9b6-0091af072225" scope="local" type="clause">S20C5</xref>.</li></ol></li><li id="_f8e0e6dc-940a-4407-95dc-1023c8368281">Class 3 buildings—<ol><li>with a Class 3 part located more than 2 <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_97c96ed5-01c7-4bfb-bc69-6899ff55a67e" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">storeys</xref> above ground level — a smoke detection system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/669_6.5.0.xml#_7d00be41-a776-4ec4-8755-875554796955" id="_b655ad69-1807-48a6-a109-e1156cc9991d" scope="local" type="clause">S20C4</xref>; or</li><li>which accommodate more than 20 residents and are the residential part of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1447_0.6.0.xml#_23515733-4511-421a-8c89-650d33e5f6e4" id="_f718f392-72b9-4215-b373-6f9d2f46cadf" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">school</xref>, accommodation for the aged, children or people with a disability — a smoke detection system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/669_6.5.0.xml#_7d00be41-a776-4ec4-8755-875554796955" id="_9fe6d01b-2ae2-49ee-ac92-a31ef5c5e4c5" scope="local" type="clause">S20C4</xref>; or</li><li>all other Class 3 buildings—<ol><li>a smoke alarm system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/667_6.4.0.xml#_994bbd6f-0202-4095-a086-46bf1e15e62a" id="_ba8e0361-1241-49b2-802c-27661c3b840a" scope="local" type="clause">S20C3</xref>; or</li><li>a smoke detection system complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/669_6.5.0.xml#_7d00be41-a776-4ec4-8755-875554796955" id="_98a9